  "tests": [
    {
      "text": "<p>Treba da napraviš novu komponentu za <code>section</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelectorAll('section')?.length === 2);"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Vaš novi element za <code>section</code> treba da dođe nakon vašeg elementa <code>.heading</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelectorAll('section')?.[1]?.previousElementSibling?.className === 'heading');"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Tvoja nova karakteristika <code>section</code> mora imati <code>class</code> postavljeno na <code>text</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelectorAll('section')?.[1]?.className === 'text');"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Treba da napraviš novu komponentu <code>p</code> unutar svoje komponente <code>.text</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelector('.text')?.querySelectorAll('p')?.length === 1);"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Tvoja nova karakteristika <code>p</code> bi trebalo da ima <code>class</code> postavljeno na <code>first-paragraph</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelector('.text p')?.className === 'first-paragraph');"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Tvoja nova funkcija za <code>p</code> treba da ima dostavljeni tekst.</p>",
      "testString": "assert(document.querySelector('.first-paragraph')?.innerText === 'Soon the freeCodeCamp curriculum will be 100% project-driven learning. Instead of a series of coding challenges, you\\'ll learn through building projects - step by step. Before we get into the details, let me emphasize: we are not changing the certifications. All 6 certifications will still have the same 5 required projects. We are only changing the optional coding challenges.');"
    }
  ],
  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ispod vašeg elementa <code>.heading</code>, kreirajte novi element <code>section</code> sa <code>class</code> podešenim na <code>text</code>. Unutar njega, kreirajte element <code>p</code> sa <code>class</code> podešenim na <code>first-paragraph</code> i sledećim tekstom:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-markup\">Soon the freeCodeCamp curriculum will be 100% project-driven learning. Instead of a series of coding challenges, you'll learn through building projects - step by step. Before we get into the details, let me emphasize: we are not changing the certifications. All 6 certifications will still have the same 5 required projects. We are only changing the optional coding challenges.\n</code></pre>\n</section>",
